{"tid":2026043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍 一架F-35A墜機 上星期同一基地另一架F-22 戰機墜毀","createTime":"2020-05-20T16:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T16:44:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"683b984174fba07331d0acfd796fbe085b5e4019","tid":2026043,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"最新更新：2020/05/20 18:46<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓20日綜合外電報導）美國佛羅里達州埃格林空軍基地（Eglin Air Force Base）官方推特帳號的一連串貼文顯示，一架美軍F-35A匿蹤戰鬥機昨晚在基地降落時墜毀。<br />\n<br />\n這座空軍基地的一則推文指出，這起事故發生在晚間9點30分前後，當時正進行「例行夜訓」。機上飛行員「成功彈跳逃生」，目前已送到第96醫務大隊，狀況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n另一則推文說：「沒有造成人命傷亡和民房受損。」這起事故已在調查中，目前不會公布飛行員姓名。<br />\n<br />\n不到一週前，埃格林空軍基地一架F-22匿蹤戰鬥機15日在訓練時墜毀，墜機地點在基地東北方12英里（約19.3公里）範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n當時基地官員表示，這架F-22的飛行員也成功彈跳逃生，狀態穩定。（譯者：陳正健/核稿：張佑之）1090520<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202005200326.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202005200326.aspx&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=a31e7111\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202005200326.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/us/f-35-stealth-fighter-jet-crashes-at-eglin-air-force-base\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Ff-35-stealth-fighter-jet-crashes-at-eglin-air-force-base&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=e423a6e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Ff-35-stealth-fighter-jet-crashes-at-eglin-air-force-base&h=e4808c8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/us/f-35-stealth-fighter-jet-crashes-at-eglin-air-force-base</a>"},{"pid":"0aa3fb5c41606cb0a7e75731fc6e864b26d21b87","tid":2026043,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"試緊新野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702ba76f2f0fdbb51433d587016ddc944df0b914","tid":2026043,"u